<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="utf-8">
  <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1, maximum-scale=1">
  <title>CRIPFCnt — About the Framework</title>
  <meta name="description" content="CRIPFCnt: an eight-pillar framework and life manual redefining consciousness, responsibility and interpretation for the AI age." />
  <link rel="canonical" href="{{siteUrl}}{{canonicalPath}}" />
  <meta property="og:site_name" content="CRIPFCnt" />
  <meta property="og:type" content="website" />
  <meta property="og:title" content="CRIPFCnt | About the Framework" />
  <meta property="og:description" content="CRIPFCnt: an eight-pillar framework and life manual redefining consciousness, responsibility and interpretation for the AI age." />
  <meta property="og:url" content="{{siteUrl}}{{canonicalPath}}" />
  <meta property="og:image" content="{{siteUrl}}/static/img/logo.png" />
  <meta name="twitter:card" content="summary_large_image" />
  <meta name="twitter:title" content="CRIPFCnt | About" />
  <meta name="twitter:image" content="{{siteUrl}}/static/img/logo.png" />

  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Crimson+Pro:ital,wght@0,400;0,600;0,700;1,400;1,700&family=Inter:wght@400;500;600;700;800&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">

  <style>
    :root {
      --navy:         #1E3A5F;
      --navy-dark:    #0F1C2E;
      --gold:         #C9A961;
      --gold-light:   #E5D4A6;
      --white:        #FFFFFF;
      --light-gray:   #F8F9FA;
      --medium-gray:  #E9ECEF;
      --dark-gray:    #495057;
      --text-primary: #212529;
      --font-serif:   'Crimson Pro', serif;
      --font-sans:    'Inter', sans-serif;
      --shadow-sm:    0 2px 8px rgba(30,58,95,0.08);
      --shadow-md:    0 4px 16px rgba(30,58,95,0.12);
      --shadow-lg:    0 8px 32px rgba(30,58,95,0.16);
    }
    *, *::before, *::after { margin:0; padding:0; box-sizing:border-box; }
    html { overflow-x:hidden; scroll-behavior:smooth; }
    body { font-family:var(--font-sans); color:var(--text-primary); line-height:1.7; background:var(--white); -webkit-font-smoothing:antialiased; overflow-x:hidden; }

    /* ── NAVBAR (identical to index) ────────────────────────────── */
    .navbar { background:var(--white); border-bottom:1px solid var(--medium-gray); padding:1.5rem 5%; position:sticky; top:0; z-index:1000; box-shadow:var(--shadow-sm); }
    .nav-container { max-width:1400px; margin:0 auto; display:flex; justify-content:space-between; align-items:center; }
    .logo { display:flex; align-items:center; gap:1rem; text-decoration:none; z-index:1001; }
    .logo-icon { width:48px; height:48px; background:var(--navy); display:flex; align-items:center; justify-content:center; font-family:var(--font-serif); font-weight:700; font-size:1.4rem; color:var(--gold); border:2px solid var(--gold); flex-shrink:0; }
    .logo-text { font-family:var(--font-serif); font-size:1.8rem; font-weight:700; color:var(--navy); letter-spacing:-0.5px; }
    .nav-links { display:flex; gap:2.5rem; list-style:none; align-items:center; }
    .nav-links a { font-size:0.95rem; font-weight:500; color:var(--text-primary); text-decoration:none; transition:color 0.3s; letter-spacing:0.3px; }
    .nav-links a:hover, .nav-links a.active { color:var(--navy); }
    .nav-cta { background:var(--navy); color:var(--white) !important; padding:0.75rem 1.75rem; border-radius:4px; font-weight:600; transition:all 0.3s; }
    .nav-cta:hover { background:var(--navy-dark) !important; }
    .user-pill { display:inline-flex; align-items:center; gap:0.6rem; padding:0.45rem 0.75rem; border:1px solid var(--medium-gray); background:var(--light-gray); border-radius:999px; font-size:0.9rem; max-width:260px; }
    .user-pill .user-email { max-width:180px; overflow:hidden; text-overflow:ellipsis; white-space:nowrap; }
    .user-pill .user-photo { width:28px; height:28px; border-radius:50%; object-fit:cover; border:1px solid var(--medium-gray); flex-shrink:0; }
    .nav-signout { background:transparent; border:1px solid var(--medium-gray); padding:0.55rem 0.9rem; border-radius:8px; font-weight:600; text-decoration:none; white-space:nowrap; color:var(--text-primary); transition:background 0.2s; }
    .nav-signout:hover { background:var(--light-gray); }
    .nav-auth { display:inline-flex; align-items:center; gap:0.75rem; }
    .nav-item.dropdown { position:relative; }
    .dropdown-toggle { display:inline-flex; align-items:center; gap:0.35rem; cursor:pointer; }
    .caret { font-size:0.75rem; opacity:0.8; transition:transform 0.2s; }
    .nav-item.dropdown.open .caret { transform:rotate(180deg); }
    .dropdown-menu { position:absolute; top:calc(100% + 8px); left:0; min-width:320px; background:var(--white); border:1px solid var(--medium-gray); box-shadow:var(--shadow-md); padding:0.6rem; border-radius:10px; opacity:0; visibility:hidden; transform:translateY(-10px); transition:all 0.2s ease; z-index:2000; pointer-events:none; }
    .nav-item.dropdown::after { content:''; position:absolute; top:100%; left:0; right:0; height:12px; display:none; }
    .nav-item.dropdown:hover::after, .nav-item.dropdown:focus-within::after { display:block; }
    .nav-item.dropdown:hover .dropdown-menu, .nav-item.dropdown:focus-within .dropdown-menu { opacity:1; visibility:visible; transform:translateY(0); pointer-events:auto; }
    .dropdown-link { display:block; text-decoration:none; padding:0.85rem 0.9rem; border-radius:8px; transition:background 0.2s; color:var(--text-primary); }
    .dropdown-link:hover { background:var(--light-gray); }
    .dd-title { font-weight:700; color:var(--navy); font-size:0.95rem; }
    .dd-sub { margin-top:0.2rem; font-size:0.82rem; color:#6b7280; }
    .mobile-menu-toggle { display:none; flex-direction:column; gap:5px; background:none; border:none; cursor:pointer; padding:0.5rem; z-index:1001; }
    .mobile-menu-toggle span { width:28px; height:3px; background:var(--navy); transition:all 0.3s; border-radius:2px; display:block; }
    .mobile-menu-toggle.active span:nth-child(1) { transform:rotate(45deg) translate(8px,8px); }
    .mobile-menu-toggle.active span:nth-child(2) { opacity:0; }
    .mobile-menu-toggle.active span:nth-child(3) { transform:rotate(-45deg) translate(7px,-7px); }

    /* ── PAGE HEADER ─────────────────────────────────────────────── */
    .page-header { background:linear-gradient(135deg, var(--navy-dark) 0%, var(--navy) 100%); padding:7rem 5% 5rem; text-align:center; position:relative; overflow:hidden; }
    .page-header::before { content:''; position:absolute; top:0; right:0; width:50%; height:100%; background:linear-gradient(90deg, transparent, rgba(201,169,97,0.05)); }
    .page-header-content { max-width:900px; margin:0 auto; position:relative; z-index:1; }
    .page-badge { display:inline-block; background:rgba(201,169,97,0.15); color:var(--gold-light); padding:0.5rem 1.25rem; border-radius:30px; font-size:0.8rem; font-weight:700; letter-spacing:1.5px; text-transform:uppercase; margin-bottom:1.75rem; border:1px solid rgba(201,169,97,0.3); }
    .page-header h1 { font-family:var(--font-serif); font-size:clamp(2.5rem,5vw,4rem); font-weight:700; color:var(--white); line-height:1.2; margin-bottom:1.25rem; }
    .page-header p { font-size:1.2rem; color:rgba(255,255,255,0.8); max-width:700px; margin:0 auto; line-height:1.7; }

    /* ── SHARED ──────────────────────────────────────────────────── */
    .section-container { max-width:1400px; margin:0 auto; }
    .section-label { font-size:0.8rem; font-weight:700; color:var(--navy); text-transform:uppercase; letter-spacing:2px; margin-bottom:0.75rem; }
    .section-title { font-family:var(--font-serif); font-size:clamp(2rem,3.5vw,2.75rem); font-weight:700; color:var(--navy-dark); line-height:1.3; margin-bottom:1.25rem; }

    /* ── OVERVIEW ─────────────────────────────────────────────────── */
    .overview-section { padding:7rem 5%; background:var(--white); }
    .overview-inner { display:grid; grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr; gap:6rem; align-items:center; }
    .overview-text p { font-size:1.05rem; color:var(--dark-gray); line-height:1.8; margin-bottom:1.25rem; }
    .overview-stat-grid { display:grid; grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr; gap:1.5rem; }
    .overview-stat { padding:2rem; border:1px solid var(--medium-gray); text-align:center; transition:all 0.3s; position:relative; overflow:hidden; }
    .overview-stat::before { content:''; position:absolute; top:0; left:0; right:0; height:3px; background:var(--gold); transform:scaleX(0); transition:transform 0.3s; }
    .overview-stat:hover::before { transform:scaleX(1); }
    .overview-stat:hover { box-shadow:var(--shadow-md); }
    .stat-val { font-family:var(--font-serif); font-size:2.5rem; font-weight:700; color:var(--gold); }
    .stat-desc { font-size:0.85rem; color:var(--dark-gray); margin-top:0.35rem; text-transform:uppercase; letter-spacing:0.5px; }
    .btn { display:inline-block; padding:1rem 2.5rem; font-family:var(--font-sans); font-size:1rem; font-weight:600; border-radius:4px; text-decoration:none; transition:all 0.3s; letter-spacing:0.3px; cursor:pointer; border:2px solid transparent; }
    .btn-navy { background:var(--navy); color:var(--white); border-color:var(--navy); }
    .btn-navy:hover { background:var(--navy-dark); border-color:var(--navy-dark); }
    .btn-gold { background:var(--gold); color:var(--navy-dark); border-color:var(--gold); }
    .btn-gold:hover { background:var(--gold-light); border-color:var(--gold-light); }

    /* ── PILLARS ─────────────────────────────────────────────────── */
    .pillars-section { padding:7rem 5%; background:var(--light-gray); }
    .pillars-section .section-header { text-align:center; margin-bottom:4rem; }
    .pillars-section .section-title { text-align:center; }
    .pillars-section .section-description { font-size:1.05rem; color:var(--dark-gray); max-width:700px; margin:0 auto; line-height:1.7; }
    .pillars-detail { display:flex; flex-direction:column; gap:1px; }
    .pillar-row { display:grid; grid-template-columns:80px 1fr 2fr; gap:2.5rem; align-items:start; background:var(--white); padding:2.5rem; border-left:4px solid transparent; transition:all 0.3s; }
    .pillar-row:hover { border-left-color:var(--gold); box-shadow:var(--shadow-sm); }
    .pillar-num { font-family:var(--font-serif); font-size:3rem; font-weight:700; color:var(--gold); opacity:0.3; line-height:1; }
    .pillar-head h3 { font-family:var(--font-serif); font-size:1.5rem; font-weight:700; color:var(--navy); margin-bottom:0.35rem; }
    .pillar-head .pillar-sub { font-size:0.8rem; font-weight:700; text-transform:uppercase; letter-spacing:1px; color:var(--gold); }
    .pillar-body p { font-size:0.95rem; color:var(--dark-gray); line-height:1.75; margin-bottom:0.75rem; }
    .pillar-apps { margin-top:1rem; }
    .pillar-apps-label { font-size:0.75rem; font-weight:700; text-transform:uppercase; letter-spacing:1px; color:var(--navy); margin-bottom:0.5rem; }
    .pillar-apps ul { list-style:none; display:flex; flex-wrap:wrap; gap:0.4rem; }
    .pillar-apps ul li { font-size:0.8rem; padding:0.2rem 0.65rem; background:var(--light-gray); border:1px solid var(--medium-gray); border-radius:2px; color:var(--dark-gray); }

    /* ── FOUNDER ─────────────────────────────────────────────────── */
    .founder-section { padding:7rem 5%; background:var(--white); }
    .founder-inner { display:grid; grid-template-columns:280px 1fr; gap:5rem; align-items:start; max-width:1100px; margin:0 auto; }
    .founder-avatar { width:280px; height:280px; background:linear-gradient(135deg, var(--navy-dark), var(--navy)); display:flex; align-items:center; justify-content:center; flex-shrink:0; }
    .founder-initials { font-family:var(--font-serif); font-size:5rem; font-weight:700; color:var(--gold); }
    .founder-info h2 { font-family:var(--font-serif); font-size:2.5rem; font-weight:700; color:var(--navy-dark); margin-bottom:0.35rem; }
    .founder-title { font-size:1.1rem; color:var(--navy); font-weight:600; margin-bottom:0.25rem; }
    .founder-credentials { font-size:0.9rem; color:var(--dark-gray); letter-spacing:0.5px; margin-bottom:2rem; padding-bottom:2rem; border-bottom:1px solid var(--medium-gray); }
    .founder-bio { font-size:1rem; color:var(--dark-gray); line-height:1.8; margin-bottom:1.1rem; }

    /* ── METHODOLOGY ─────────────────────────────────────────────── */
    .methodology-section { padding:7rem 5%; background:linear-gradient(135deg, var(--navy-dark), var(--navy)); color:var(--white); }
    .methodology-section .section-title { color:var(--white); text-align:center; margin-bottom:3.5rem; }
    .methodology-grid { display:grid; grid-template-columns:repeat(3,1fr); gap:2rem; max-width:1100px; margin:0 auto; }
    .method-card { border:1px solid rgba(201,169,97,0.3); padding:2.5rem 2rem; background:rgba(255,255,255,0.03); transition:background 0.3s; }
    .method-card:hover { background:rgba(201,169,97,0.07); }
    .method-icon { font-size:2.25rem; margin-bottom:1.25rem; }
    .method-title { font-family:var(--font-serif); font-size:1.4rem; font-weight:700; color:var(--gold-light); margin-bottom:0.75rem; }
    .method-text { font-size:0.95rem; color:rgba(255,255,255,0.75); line-height:1.7; }

    /* ── CTA ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────── */
    .cta-section { background:var(--navy); padding:6rem 5%; text-align:center; }
    .cta-container { max-width:800px; margin:0 auto; }
    .cta-section h2 { font-family:var(--font-serif); font-size:clamp(2rem,4vw,3rem); font-weight:700; color:var(--white); margin-bottom:1.25rem; }
    .cta-section p { font-size:1.1rem; color:rgba(255,255,255,0.85); margin-bottom:2.5rem; line-height:1.7; }
    .cta-buttons { display:flex; gap:1.25rem; justify-content:center; flex-wrap:wrap; }
    .btn-primary { background:var(--gold); color:var(--navy-dark); border:2px solid var(--gold); }
    .btn-primary:hover { background:var(--gold-light); border-color:var(--gold-light); }
    .btn-secondary { background:transparent; color:var(--white); border:2px solid var(--white); }
    .btn-secondary:hover { background:var(--white); color:var(--navy); }

    /* ── FOOTER ──────────────────────────────────────────────────── */
    footer { background:var(--navy-dark); color:rgba(255,255,255,0.8); padding:5rem 5% 3rem; }
    .footer-container { max-width:1400px; margin:0 auto; }
    .footer-grid { display:grid; grid-template-columns:2fr 1fr 1fr 1fr; gap:4rem; margin-bottom:4rem; }
    .footer-brand { font-family:var(--font-serif); font-size:2rem; font-weight:700; color:var(--gold); margin-bottom:1.25rem; }
    .footer-description { color:rgba(255,255,255,0.65); line-height:1.7; margin-bottom:1.25rem; font-size:0.95rem; }
    .footer-title { font-family:var(--font-serif); font-size:1.05rem; font-weight:700; color:var(--white); margin-bottom:1.25rem; }
    .footer-links { list-style:none; }
    .footer-links li { margin-bottom:0.6rem; font-size:0.9rem; color:rgba(255,255,255,0.6); }
    .footer-links a { color:rgba(255,255,255,0.65); text-decoration:none; transition:color 0.3s; }
    .footer-links a:hover { color:var(--gold); }
    .footer-bottom { border-top:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.1); padding-top:2rem; text-align:center; color:rgba(255,255,255,0.5); font-size:0.875rem; }
    .footer-bottom a { color:rgba(255,255,255,0.6); text-decoration:none; }
    .footer-bottom a:hover { color:var(--gold); }

    /* ── MOBILE ──────────────────────────────────────────────────── */
    @media (max-width:768px) {
      html, body { overflow-x:hidden; width:100%; }
      .mobile-menu-toggle { display:flex; }
      .nav-links { position:fixed; top:0; right:-85%; width:85%; max-width:320px; height:100vh; background:var(--white); flex-direction:column; align-items:flex-start; padding:5rem 1.5rem 2rem; gap:0; box-shadow:-4px 0 20px rgba(0,0,0,0.1); transition:right 0.3s ease; overflow-y:auto; overflow-x:hidden; z-index:1000; box-sizing:border-box; }
      .nav-links.active { right:0; }
      body.menu-open { overflow:hidden; position:fixed; width:100%; }
      body::after { content:''; position:fixed; top:0; left:0; width:100%; height:100%; background:rgba(0,0,0,0.5); opacity:0; visibility:hidden; transition:all 0.3s; z-index:999; }
      body.menu-open::after { opacity:1; visibility:visible; }
      .nav-links li { width:100%; border-bottom:1px solid var(--medium-gray); box-sizing:border-box; }
      .nav-links li:last-child { border-bottom:none; }
      .nav-links a { display:block; padding:1.1rem 0; width:100%; font-size:1rem; box-sizing:border-box; }
      .nav-cta { margin-top:1rem; text-align:center; width:100%; box-sizing:border-box; }
      .nav-item.dropdown { width:100%; }
      .nav-item.dropdown::after { display:none !important; }
      .dropdown-toggle { width:100%; justify-content:space-between; padding:1.1rem 0; display:flex; }
      .dropdown-menu { position:static; opacity:1; visibility:visible; transform:none; display:none; width:100%; min-width:0; box-shadow:none; border:none; padding:0.5rem 0 1rem; pointer-events:auto; background:var(--light-gray); border-radius:0; }
      .nav-item.dropdown.open .dropdown-menu { display:block !important; }
      .nav-links li.nav-auth { flex-direction:column; align-items:stretch; gap:0.6rem; }
      .nav-links li.nav-auth .user-pill, .nav-links li.nav-auth .nav-signout { width:100%; }
      .mobile-only { display:block !important; }
      .desktop-only { display:none !important; }
      .mobile-lms-section { width:100%; }
      .mobile-section-header { font-size:0.72rem; font-weight:700; text-transform:uppercase; letter-spacing:1.5px; color:var(--dark-gray); padding:1.5rem 0 0.75rem; border-top:2px solid var(--medium-gray); margin-top:1rem; }
      .mobile-lms-links { list-style:none; padding:0; margin:0; width:100%; }
      .mobile-lms-links a { display:block; padding:0.9rem 0.75rem; font-size:0.9rem; color:var(--text-primary); background:var(--light-gray); margin:0.25rem 0; border-radius:8px; }
      .overview-inner { grid-template-columns:1fr; gap:3rem; }
      .pillar-row { grid-template-columns:50px 1fr; gap:1.25rem; }
      .pillar-body { grid-column:1/-1; }
      .founder-inner { grid-template-columns:1fr; gap:2.5rem; }
      .founder-avatar { width:200px; height:200px; }
      .methodology-grid { grid-template-columns:1fr; }
      .footer-grid { grid-template-columns:1fr; gap:2.5rem; }
      .overview-stat-grid { grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr; }
    }
    @media (min-width:769px) { .mobile-only { display:none !important; } .desktop-only { display:block !important; } }

    .reveal { opacity:0; transform:translateY(20px); transition:opacity 0.6s ease, transform 0.6s ease; }
    .reveal.visible { opacity:1; transform:translateY(0); }
  </style>
</head>
<body>

<!-- ── NAVBAR ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────── -->
<nav class="navbar">
  <div class="nav-container">
    <a href="/" class="logo">
      <div class="logo-icon">C</div>
      <span class="logo-text">CRIPFCnt</span>
    </a>
    <button class="mobile-menu-toggle" id="mobileMenuToggle" aria-label="Toggle menu">
      <span></span><span></span><span></span>
    </button>
    <ul class="nav-links" id="navLinks">
      <li><a href="/">Home</a></li>
      <li><a href="/about" class="active">Framework</a></li>
      <li><a href="/services">Services</a></li>
      <li><a href="/scoi">Audits</a></li>
      <li class="nav-item dropdown desktop-only" id="lmsDropdown">
        <a href="/lms" class="dropdown-toggle">LMS <span class="caret">▾</span></a>
        <div class="dropdown-menu">
          <a class="dropdown-link" href="/auth/parent"><div class="dd-title">Parents &amp; Guardians</div><div class="dd-sub">Manage kids · Grades 1–7 + High School</div></a>
          <a class="dropdown-link" href="/auth/teacher"><div class="dd-title">Private Teachers</div><div class="dd-sub">Up to 15/40 learners</div></a>
          <a class="dropdown-link" href="/auth/google?returnTo=%2Forg%2Fcripfcnt-school%2Fdashboard&force=1"><div class="dd-title">Professionals</div><div class="dd-sub">8 modules · audits · certification</div></a>
        </div>
      </li>
      <li class="mobile-only mobile-lms-section">
        <div class="mobile-section-header">LMS Options</div>
        <ul class="mobile-lms-links">
          <li><a href="/auth/parent">👨‍👩‍👧 Parents &amp; Guardians</a></li>
          <li><a href="/auth/teacher">👨‍🏫 Private Teachers</a></li>
          <li><a href="/auth/google?returnTo=%2Forg%2Fcripfcnt-school%2Fdashboard&force=1">🏛️ Professionals</a></li>
        </ul>
      </li>
      <li><a href="/auth/school">Student Portal</a></li>
      <li><a href="/contact">Contact</a></li>
      <li class="nav-auth">
        {{#if user}}
          <div class="user-pill" title="{{user.email}}">
            {{#if user.photo}}<img class="user-photo" src="{{user.photo}}" alt="Profile" />{{/if}}
            <span class="user-email">{{#if user.email}}{{user.email}}{{else}}{{user.displayName}}{{/if}}</span>
          </div>
          <a href="/auth/logout" class="nav-signout">Sign out</a>
        {{else}}
          <a href="mailto:info@cripfcnt.com" class="nav-cta">Get Started</a>
        {{/if}}
      </li>
    </ul>
  </div>
</nav>

<!-- ── PAGE HEADER ────────────────────────────────────────────────────── -->
<header class="page-header">
  <div class="page-header-content">
    <div class="page-badge">Intelligence Structuring Framework</div>
    <h1>About CRIPFCnt</h1>
    <p>A comprehensive eight-pillar framework for recalibrating human intelligence, governance structures, and institutional effectiveness in the AI age.</p>
  </div>
</header>

<!-- ── OVERVIEW ───────────────────────────────────────────────────────── -->
<section class="overview-section">
  <div class="section-container">
    <div class="overview-inner">
      <div class="overview-text reveal">
        <div class="section-label">What is CRIPFCnt?</div>
        <h2 class="section-title">Recalibrating Intelligence for a Changing World</h2>
        <p>CRIPFCnt is an eight-pillar framework — Consciousness, Responsibility, Interpretation, Purpose, Frequencies, Civilization, Negotiation, and Technology — developed to address a fundamental gap between human intelligence and the demands of modern institutional life.</p>
        <p>Developed by Donald Mataranyika, Chartered Secretary and Governance Specialist, the framework provides structured methodologies for organizations, leaders, and individuals navigating complex governance environments, systemic inequality, and rapid technological change.</p>
        <p>Beyond institutional reform, CRIPFCnt introduces the Social Contract Obligation Index (SCOI) — a measurable system for evaluating structural contribution, visibility, and environmental resilience at the individual and organizational level.</p>
        <a href="/services" class="btn btn-navy" style="margin-top:1.5rem;">Explore Services →</a>
      </div>
